p://reliefweb.int/report/ethiopia/unicef-supports-fight-end-marriage-abduction-ethiopia|title=UNICEF supports fight to end marriage by abduction in Ethiopia|publisher=reliefweb.int|date=2004-11-09|accessdate=2013-08-29|archive-date=2013-09-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130921060900/http://reliefweb.int/report/ethiopia/unicef-supports-fight-end-marriage-abduction-ethiopia|dead-url=no}}</ref>

[[骗婚|骗婚]]是利用婚姻来获得某种社会或法律好处（常常与移民身份有关）。虽然这些婚姻获得双方当事人的同意。在欧盟有一种人口贩卖，为留学生或欧盟雇工（常常来自亚洲国家）供给新娘（常常来自前共产主义国家，现为欧盟成员国——特别是巴尔干地区国家）以便他们能留在欧洲。<ref>{{cite news | url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-europe-11792437 | work=BBC News | title=Latvia calls on Ireland to tackle sham marriages | date=2010-11-21 | accessdate=2014-08-28 | archive-date=2014-02-22 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140222054659/http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-europe-11792437 | dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news | url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-europe-11808069 | work=BBC News | title=Latvia appeals to Ireland to stop sham marriages | date=2010-11-22 | accessdate=2014-08-28 | archive-date=2014-02-20 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140220020930/http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-europe-11808069 | dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://eurojust.europa.eu/doclibrary/Eurojust-framework/Casework/Eurojust%20action%20against%20trafficking%20in%20human%20beings%20%28October%202012%29/THB-report-2012-10-18-EN.pdf |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2014-08-28 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140906210733/http://eurojust.europa.eu/doclibrary/Eurojust-framework/Casework/Eurojust%20action%20against%20trafficking%20in%20human%20beings%20%28October%202012%29/THB-report-2012-10-18-EN.pdf |archivedate=2014-09-06 }}</ref>

